LightScope is a network security monitoring tool that detects unwanted
network traffic and provides honeypot functionality.

Features:
- Captures and analyzes blocked TCP SYN packets via pflog
- Configurable honeypot ports with PROXY protocol forwarding
- Uploads security telemetry to thelightscope.com for analysis
- Privacy-preserving IP randomization

WWW: https://thelightscope.com
